# R-AI_agent

A simple Python-based AI agent project designed to perform tasks using modular tools and scripts.

## ğŸš€ Overview

This repository contains code for a basic AI agent built in Python.  
At its core, the agent logic is defined in `main.py` and extended with helper tools in `tools.py`.  
The project is intended as a starting point for experimentation with AI-driven workflows and automation.

